T1  - Profiting from innovation when digital business ecosystems emerge: A control point perspective
AU  - Bohnsack, René
AU  - Rennings, Michael
AU  - Block, Carolin
AU  - Bröring, Stefanie
JO  - Research Policy
VL  - 53
IS  - 3
SP  - 104961
